						<p><strong>As it turns out, it’s not easy.</strong></p>
						<p>First up, why would you put a server on a Pacific island, anyway?</p>
						<p>Imagine this: you’re a gamer living in Sydney.</p>
						<p>You want to play games with your friends Alice and Bob, who live in Singapore and Japan respectively — but there’s a problem:</p>
